💼 Employee Management System (Java)
📌 Project Overview

The Employee Management System is a desktop-based application developed using Java (Swing & AWT). It helps organizations manage employee records efficiently, including adding employees, viewing details, attendance management, and user authentication (Login/Signup).

This project is suitable for beginners to understand Java GUI development and basic CRUD operations.

🚀 Features
🔐 User Authentication (Login & Signup)
➕ Add New Employees
👨‍💼 View Employee Details
📊 Employee Dashboard
🕒 Attendance Management
🚪 Logout Functionality
🎨 GUI-based Interface using Swing
🛠️ Technologies Used
Java (JDK 8+)
Swing & AWT (GUI)
OOP Concepts
Event Handling
