└── (Image & assets)
▶️ How to Run the Project

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/EmployeeManagementSystem.git
Open the project in any Java IDE:
IntelliJ IDEA
Eclipse
NetBeans
Compile and run the project:
Start from SplashScreen.java or LoginFrame.java
🔑 Default Workflow
Open application
Signup (if new user)
Login
Access Dashboard
Add/View Employees
Manage Attendance
Logout
